| c1   | c2   | count(*) |
+------+------+----------+
|    1 |    1 |       13 |
|    1 |    2 |       12 |
|    2 |    1 |       15 |
|    2 |    2 |       14 |
|    3 |    1 |       13 |
|    3 |    2 |        8 |
|    4 |    1 |        9 |
|    4 |    2 |       16 |
+------+------+----------+
